&lt;li&gt;Build and optimize Salesforce Flows using best-practice patterns (bulkification, limits awareness, error handling).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain security models, user access, profiles, permission sets, and role hierarchies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the creation and refinement of reports, dashboards, and list views.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with CPQ, case management, lead routing, and other GTM workflows as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Platform Maintenance &amp;amp; Data Quality&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor system health and troubleshoot user issues, data errors, and automation failures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform data updates, uploads, deduplication, cleansing, and quality monitoring.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain sandbox environments—including refresh cycles, testing coordination, and metadata cleanliness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate on system audits, optimization efforts, and routine administrative maintenance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Solution Delivery &amp;amp; Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Business Systems Analysts to understand requirements, user stories, and use cases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate requirements into well-structured technical solutions aligned with platform best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Salesforce Developers when custom code or advanced components are required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in design discussions, estimating effort and identifying edge cases or downstream impacts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Testing, Deployment &amp;amp; Documentation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and execute test cases for admin-built changes; assist with UAT coordination.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support release management processes: change documentation, version tracking, deployment validation, and end-user support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain admin-level documentation for configurations, workflows, data models, and processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure traceability between business requirements and delivered solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Training, Support &amp;amp; User Enablement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide day-to-day support for Salesforce users across Sales, Marketing, Support, and other departments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver short trainings, demos, and walkthroughs to help users adopt new features or workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop user-facing guides, FAQs, and quick-reference materials.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify recurring user issues and recommend automation or process changes to reduce friction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
