&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is a hands-on technical builder with a strong understanding of Salesforce development best practices, an eye for scalable design, and the drive to translate business needs into high-impact system functionality. While technical skills take priority, the role also requires clear communication and close collaboration with stakeholders and the Business Operations team.&lt;/p&gt;
