&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the development of declarative and programmatic solutions that improve GTM efficiencies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help maintain integration points between Salesforce and GTM systems (HubSpot, databases, APIs, Workato), escalating complex cases as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ownership of delivery quality. Participate in code reviews, version control, and deployment processes (CI/CD).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with other developers, admins, analysts, and the Director of Business Operations to implement system enhancements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with business stakeholders to understand their needs, troubleshoot issues, and implement iterative improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate business and functional requirements into technical solutions with appropriate documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical support and guidance to admins and analysts when issues relate to code-driven functionality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Troubleshooting &amp;amp; Continuous Improvement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
