&lt;li&gt;Monitor system performance, data integrity, and automation reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to streamline processes, reduce technical debt, and improve maintainability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current with Salesforce platform releases and recommend enhancements that add value.&lt;/li&gt;
